20606 US Route 23, Greenup, Kentucky 41144, United States
routes.directions:
1. Look for traffic as you cross US 23. Be safe!
2. Follow Ohio River Road for approximately 1 mile.
3. Continue following the road, do not take any turns. Enjoy the wildflowers and intermittent shade.
4. As the road ends, look to your left. Enjoy the decrepit church and wonder what it was like in the old days!
